schools.name: Palm Bay Magnet Senior High School

data.description: Seller Motivated! Will allow closing cost credit of 2500 with full price offer! This spacious 2 bdrm townhome has had some very nice updates that we hope you will appreciate!  Fencing around the private courtyard replaced in summer of 2018 with extensions for storage.  Open the gate and check out the portable hot tub perfect for a soak and stargazing after a long day at work!  Electrical upgrade to exterior service line and 220 capacity installed.  Modern dusk to dawn lighting in patio area and new exterior paint not to mention the vinyl cheeks and soffit on the Mansard roof system. New water heater 2020, new HVAC system 2019 and upgraded 7.5mm LVP with gold underlayment in living spaces excluding laundry room and bathroom which is tiled. New stained wood on stairway. Close to L3Harris, shopping, dining and I95. Kitchen and Full bath need updating, reflected in price
